# Sentinel Guardian 🛡️
**The Security Layer for QAIzero Orchestration**

## Overview
**Sentinel Guardian** is a high-performance security module designed to provide tamper detection and system integrity for the **QAIzero** adaptive AI engine. It ensures that the local inference environment remains secure, hardware-agnostic, and resilient against unauthorized modifications.

## Key Features
* **QAIzero Integration:** Built specifically to protect the QAIzero orchestration engine.
* **Proactive Tamper Detection:** Advanced monitoring to identify and mitigate system breaches in real-time.
* **Resource Efficient:** Engineered for minimal overhead, maintaining the QAIzero philosophy of efficiency.
* **Integrity Assurance:** Validates the state of the local inference stack.

## Quick Start
```bash
# Clone the repository
git clone [https://github.com/alejandro/sentinel-guardian.git](https://github.com/alejandro/sentinel-guardian.git)

# Initialize the module
python sentinel_init.py --mode autonomous
